INSTALL ANGULAR

1. sudo npm install -g @angular/cli
2. ng new my-dream-app
3. route to angular > yes
4. stylesheet > CSS
5. cd my-dream-app
6. ng serve
7. run the url at your browser (localhost:4200)
8. OPen the folder of my-dream-app in VS Code
9. src > app > app.component.html

-->app.component.ts
is variable

--> install in terminal, then go to app.module.ts add import
ng g component products
ng g class product --> new class is new data type
ng g service http (normally no "s" singular)

what you define in product.ts in product.component.ts array shall be the same

--> products.component.html
*ngFor="let item of items" (let singular of plural) --> for loop
*ngIf="selectedProduct" --> show only if product is selected 

pipes angular
| <-- "pipe" will format the left side with the formater of right side

